{"word":"ἄγλωσσος","slug":"ἄγλωσσος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄγλωσσος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γλῶσσα'><el>γλῶσσα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>without tongue</i>, of the crocodile, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>tongueless, ineloquent</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>elinguis</el>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>: then = <a href='S:βάρβαρος'><el>βάρβαρος</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}